Data and Code for the X/Twitter BlueSky Weibo paper.

Files:
Chinese_BERT_model - are the config and tokenization files for the BERT model used, the model itself is too large to directly upload to GitHub

Country_Counts - are the output files for the country counts over time for the two periods and both languages, this are the total counts for
every country mentioned which the Top 10 and Top 5 analyses are based off.

Country_Map_Codes - are the Jupyter notebooks for the code used for the various inital analyses in both English and Chinese in terms of map 
making and overall sentiment analysis.

Country_Sentiment - is the Jupyter notebook for calculating the sentiment associated with the top five countries 

Data_anon - are the anonymous data files containing the posts from Weibo, X/Twitter, and BlueSky, they contain the sentiment of the posts, but 
no information linking back to the user. 
